data.title: Travels of Former Gov. Mitt Romney
data.text:
Former Gov. Mitt Romney | President Barack Obama

Romney continued his intensive fundraising, holding more than 30 fundraisers during the month in addtion to the "First National Romney Victory Leadership Retreat," a three-day event for major donors in Deer Valley, UT.
